Luis Barletta as administrator of Empresa Distribuidora de
Energia Sur SA, or Edesur.  Barletta will oversee the electricity distributor for the
next 45 days, according to resolution 183/2012 issued by
electricity regulator ENRE.  The company missed a 150 million-peso ($33 million) payment
this week to wholesaler Cammesa and had sought funds from state-
owned Banco de la Nacion Argentina, Ambito Financiero reported
